Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Linux Hello Team <dev@linuxhello.local>
Installed-Size: 17
Depends: dbus, systemd
Conflicts: linux-hello-gui
Section: system
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/linuxhello/face-auth
Description: Face Authentication System for Linux
 Linux Hello provides facial recognition authentication for:
 .
  * sudo authentication
  * screenlock unlock (KDE/GNOME)
  * login screen (future)
 .
 This package includes the daemon and PAM module.
